category: Libs
requires: cygwin libglib2.0_0 libjson-glib1.0_0 libsoup2.4_1
external-source: geocode-glib
sdesc: "GLib geocoding library that uses the Yahoo! Place Finder service (runtime)"
ldesc: "geocode-glib is a convenience library for the Yahoo! Place Finder
APIs, as described at:
http://developer.yahoo.com/geo/placefinder/

The Place Finder web service allows to do geocoding (finding longitude
and latitude from an address), and reverse geocoding (finding an address
from coordinates)."
